      <title>菲律宾的贸易负责人说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/philippines-mulls-cutting-tariffs-on-us-products-trade-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾贸易负责人说，菲律宾正在考虑减少对美国产品的关税，以应对唐纳德·特朗普总统的全面征税，包括对马尼拉商品的关税17％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/philippines-mulls-cutting-tariffs-on-us-products-trade-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 07:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
